---
import SectionLayout from "../layouts/SectionLayout.astro";
---

<SectionLayout id="kind-words" pageIndex={4} pageTitle="Kind Words">
  <div class="kind-words__grid">
    <figure class="kind-words__card">
      <blockquote class="kind-words__quote">
        "Cassi's the reason we were able to do a 4-domain + CMS migration as
        well as a complete brand overhaul entirely in-house in 1 year, saving
        Submittable an incredible amount of money and time. She's a strong
        strategic partner, skilled at translating technical ideas and issues to
        non-technical marketing teams. Also just a wonderful, fun person to work
        with."
      </blockquote>
      <figcaption class="kind-words__attribution">
        <span class="kind-words__name">Whitney Rhodes</span>
        <span class="kind-words__title"
          >Director of Organic Growth, Submittable</span
        >
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <figure class="kind-words__card">
      <blockquote class="kind-words__quote">
        "Cassi was such a great partner to work with, especially where design
        and development meet. She was always easy to collaborate with, super
        accommodating, and genuinely focused on finding solutions that worked
        for both of us. She offered thoughtful feedback on designs and often
        helped shape ideas in ways that strengthened the final result. Beyond
        her talent, Cassi is just a fun, outgoing person who brings great energy
        to every meeting and conversation. Any team would be lucky to have her."
      </blockquote>
      <figcaption class="kind-words__attribution">
        <span class="kind-words__name">Raymond Lombardi</span>
        <span class="kind-words__title">Art Director, Submittable</span>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</SectionLayout>

<style>
  .kind-words {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .kind-words__container {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 1600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 0 5rem;
  }

  .kind-words__header {
    border-top: 2px solid currentColor;
    padding-top: var(--space-s);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .kind-words__label {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .kind-words__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 10rem;
  }

  .kind-words__card {
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .kind-words__quote {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .kind-words__attribution {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .kind-words__name {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .kind-words__title {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .kind-words__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
